text: but thou shalt eat them before the Lord thy God, in the place which the Lord thy God shall choose, thou and thy son and thy daughter, and thy manservant and maidservant, and the love-vite that dwelleth in thy cities, and thou shalt rejoice and be refreshed before the Lord thy God in all things, where unto thou shalt put thy hand.
